songs.title: We Can’t Fly - Radio Edit
songs.lyrics:
We can fly, come on let’s try
We’re boys and girls
Who rule the world
We can fly, or kiss the sky
So long, bye bye…

(We can oh oh we can) – repeat

We can fly, come on let’s try
We’re boys and girls
Who rule the world

We can fly, or kiss the sky
So long, bye bye
Come on don’t cry

(We can oh oh we can)
We can fly, come on let’s try
We’re boys and girls
Who rule the world
